  title="190 Million Women Have Endometriosis. It Gets a Fifth of the Funding It Should."
  description="Endometriosis affects 190 million women worldwide, yet receives less than a fifth of the research funding its disease burden justifies. New treatments and diagnostic tools are finally emerging."
